  <paragraphs>
    <title><custom ref="reflection-quest-titulo"/></title>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Which students came up with an unexpected strategy in today’s lesson? What are some ways you can be more open to the ideas of each and every student?</p>
  </paragraphs>
